<subSubSection pageId="17" pageNumber="18" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="17.[94,719,1978,2131]" lastBlockId="17.[794,1418,218,339]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[94,205,1978,2003]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Remarks:</emphasis>
Species described on a single male labelled ‘ 
<collectingCountry box="[97,162,2010,2035]" name="Brazil" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Brésil</collectingCountry>
, Santarem’, preserved in NHMB. No other specimens are known so far. The 
<typeStatus box="[433,534,2042,2067]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">holotype</typeStatus>
lacks some tarsi and last antennomeres. The specimens collected in 
<collectingCountry box="[94,262,2106,2131]" name="French Guiana" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">French Guiana</collectingCountry>
, initially named as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Brancucci" authorityYear="1981" box="[490,680,2106,2131]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Macromalthinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="santaremensis">
<emphasis box="[490,680,2106,2131]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">M. santaremensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by Constantin (2016), are similar to the male 
<typeStatus box="[1285,1386,218,243]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">holotype</typeStatus>
in the body shape and genitalia, but additional material reveals new elusive characters leading to the description of 
<taxonomicName authority="Biffi &amp; Constantin, 2018" authorityName="Biffi &amp; Constantin" authorityYear="2018" box="[794,945,314,339]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Macromalthinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="guyanensis" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[794,945,314,339]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">M. guyanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[950,1008,314,339]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Biffi &amp; Constantin, 2018" authorityName="Biffi &amp; Constantin" authorityYear="2018" box="[1061,1208,314,339]" class="Insecta" family="Cantharidae" genus="Macromalthinus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="orapuensis" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[1061,1208,314,339]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">M. orapuensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1214,1272,314,339]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
